{"about_the_game":"<strong>The Monster Mole</strong> is an <strong>asymmetrical first-person PvP horror survival</strong> game where you either try to survive and escape a vicious beast with your teammates, or hunt your prey as the <strong>nearly-blind</strong> monster that inhabits the surroundings of the fictional town of Dry Lake.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1572150/extras/MonsterMoleRoofCrawlingGIF.gif?t=1685039403\" /><br><br>As a survivor, coordinating with your teammates and finding the right balance between being quick and being quiet is key to escaping with your life.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find spare parts and repair your car;<br></li><li> Alternatively, find and fuel the generator and escape on foot;<br></li><li> Understand the balance between being loud but quick and quiet but slow;<br></li><li> Slow down and confound the beast - turn on radios, set down bear traps, collect and throw stones to draw it away from you;<br></li><li> Know when to speak - communication is important, but the monster is always listening!<br></li><li> Learn to navigate the dark, foggy maps avoiding their many traps.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1572150/extras/SurvivorFixingCarDoor.gif?t=1685039403\" /><br><br>As the Mole, mastering your understanding of the environmental clues and sounds made by the survivors will more than make up for your limited sight.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Make up for your near-sightedness by listening attentively for sounds;<br></li><li> Leave behind gooey traps that reveal and slow down survivors;<br></li><li> Destroy tools that would otherwise be helpful to the thrill-seekers and knock down doors to houses where they might have barricaded themselves within;<br></li><li> Keep the pressure on! The survivors have a limited time to escape, force them into making mistakes by always being on the move.</li></ul